        "query": "=UPDATE subscribers\nSET email = COALESCE($3, email),\n    nom = COALESCE($4, nom),\n    prenom = COALESCE($5, prenom),\n    telephone = COALESCE($6, telephone),\n    entreprise = COALESCE($7, entreprise),\n    tags = COALESCE($8, tags),\n    status = COALESCE($9, status),\n    updated_at = NOW()\nWHERE id = $1::uuid AND tenant_id = $2::uuid\nRETURNING id, tenant_id as tenantId, email, telephone, nom, prenom, entreprise, status, source, tags, created_at as createdAt, updated_at as updatedAt",
